{"tid":140520,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖多字) 山西 - 懸空寺 + 民間故宮王家大院 + 壺口瀑布","createTime":"2017-03-02T09:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T16:38:05.000Z","uid":16697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e72747e0079948ee4dac92371b4fdcc036bd776d","tid":140520,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"山西有咩玩?<br />\n太原 :  山西省會,山入靠晒佢,著名景點:晉祠,最撚出名架啦<br />\n大同: 懸空寺,雲崗石窟,上,下華嚴寺,九龍壁<br />\n平遙:平遙古城,雙林寺,喬家大院<br />\n平遙古城同其他江南古城唔同,入面仲有好多當地人生活緊,感覺較為樸素,但都相當商業化啦<br />\n介休: 王家大院,張壁古堡,王家大院真係痴撚線,民間故宮,好撚大,<br />\n臨汾:壺口瀑布,冇想像中咁震撼<br />\n仲有蹟口,運城等等<br />\n<br />\n簡介:懸空寺:懸空寺，位於中華人民共和國山西省大同市渾源縣，是一座儒釋道三教合一的寺廟。該寺始建於北魏年間，現存建築均為明清時期重建。整座寺廟建於翠峰山的半山腰上，依靠27根木樑支撐全部寺廟主要建築，遠看形如懸在半空，故名懸空寺。整座寺廟共有40間房屋，為木質框架式結構，主體建築之間由走廊和棧道相連.旺季（3月1日-10月31日）：124元/人（門票24元，登臨費100元），半票65元（門票15元，登臨費50元）；<br />\n淡季（11月1日-次年2月）：115元（門票15元，登臨費100元），半票63元（門票13元，登臨費55元）；<br />\n<br />\n講下點解我會去呢,好細個睇紀錄片見到,已經留下好撚深刻印象,同感覺好撚驚,咁既樓都有,係懸崖上面,之後讀書就無乜點理啦,前排又無意中睇到,就自己一個去玩啦,去左8日,玩埋山西(香港&gt;太原&gt;大同&gt;臨汾壺口瀑布&gt;介休&gt;平遙&gt;太原&gt;香港)<br />\n<br />\n香港港最快係搭港航飛機到太原再坐大巴大約四小時去到大同,大同再坐車就2小時左右啦,去到天氣幾好,唔似傳聞中成個天空都係媒,但真係多運媒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到車真係驚,非旺季去,唔多人,旅行團上午走晒,我下午先去,但多人行果陣FEEL到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,旺季時聽講限人數,好撚多人排隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksfyq23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fksfyq23.jpg&h=c16be7a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2u1267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2u1267.jpg&h=feb8f420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0UBRfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0UBRfZ.jpg&h=69034f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Geh2G97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeh2G97.jpg&h=4db258bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvZsX32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvZsX32.jpg&h=72f7781f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GWc35G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GWc35G.jpg&h=7b795377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAYQ146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAYQ146.jpg&h=e8e9556a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L250tVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL250tVE.jpg&h=62a051ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王家大院: :&ldquo;王家歸來不看院&rdquo;名副其實，無人不被它精湛的雕刻藝術、大氣的空間格局深深吸引。<br />\n這座被譽為&ldquo;華夏民居第一宅&rdquo;的晉商大院，是由靜升王氏耗費半個世紀修建而成的豪華住宅。王家大院大得超出一般人想像，由高家崖、紅門堡組成兩個相對封閉的院落，兩院之間由一座細長的橋騰空連起，其餘又由無數四合院組合而成。最值得細細品味的是高家崖，這一座封閉式的城堡式建築，又名&ldquo;中國民居藝術館&rdquo;，依山而建，氣勢宏偉。有院落26座，房屋212間，可分為前後兩院，整體佈局承襲了中國古代前堂後室的結構，既增強了安全度，又開闊了庭院的空間。前院是社交場所，從門口到室內到處可見精美的磚雕、石雕、木雕。後院則是主人的生活區，仍以各種雕刻為主要裝飾，精美雅緻。紅門堡與高家崖東西相望，因堡門是紅色的，故而得名。堡內特色鮮明、內涵豐富的石雕融南北風情於一體，是清代雕刻藝術的典範。門票66元/人，學生證半價、70歲老人憑證件免票、60-70歲老人<br />\n憑證件半價；導遊80元/次開放時間夏季：8:00-19:00；冬季：8:00-17:00<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6NCf86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6NCf86.jpg&h=292e0b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Ui2kE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Ui2kE4.jpg&h=8a19bb19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94ESMvM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94ESMvM.jpg&h=84071223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebXgZJw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebXgZJw.jpg&h=33e89251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWJ47CY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWJ47CY.jpg&h=cedb0ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRLQst5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRLQst5.jpg&h=a09e74a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvgwM7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvgwM7M.jpg&h=13c96f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Gc288Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Gc288Q.jpg&h=8773bc49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rve99qJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frve99qJ.jpg&h=6c1baea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oH0NF29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoH0NF29.jpg&h=f18f1ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3J4YPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3J4YPf.jpg&h=f822d361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7SeP7rg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SeP7rg.jpg&h=69fe1c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3020u1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3020u1f.jpg&h=6aa6e86e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0o8V44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0o8V44.jpg&h=804e2c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總括來講,山西唔係旅遊熱門省份,但睇人文古蹟真係幾好,岩晒我呢D好歷史既<br />\n我最鍾意係懸空寺 , 王家大院,雲崗石窟 &amp; 平遙古城<br />\n不過平遙成撚日停電,住3晚,停2晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp2xtE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp2xtE0.jpg&h=cab3b195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6032vW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6032vW.jpg&h=efa16ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nW8o8JM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnW8o8JM.jpg&h=3508e135&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d52088f91f311f000ab8ef79933c1272c667bc9c","tid":140520,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"大陸真係冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9db517641cce33b5d9404a8fdd38062fc7f802","tid":140520,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:45:26.000Z","msg":"支持 , 其實大陸d 景唔差<br />\n不過連登鐘意日韓台多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c2590f28b7125f5e22075d66f008076fb6747b","tid":140520,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"頂個懸空寺真係行到我腳震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw留個靚名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d3d0c59e3c9bbe9cba281119cb1b688bd84488","tid":140520,"uid":78009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"環境上嘅靚係事實，有人文風景係事實，但好憎現時嘅環境同呢個國家嘅人更加係事實"},{"pid":"721c75bcc0192098178374652c32c2fad36ee878","tid":140520,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2G7Zcf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2G7Zcf0.jpg&h=b53ced39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸永遠搞到d古跡不論不類，門前d花埔邊會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ec08f32603d5e9f6c02593eea1e68a7fe9a31b","tid":140520,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d925a4e92c1d10cd3202920b996c3e216143ade5","tid":140520,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"冇啦?"}]}